754
00:51:02,080 --> 00:51:02,960
Pa vjerojatno je sportaš.

755
00:51:03,600 --> 00:51:05,120
Vjerojatno mu je stalo do kondicije.

756
00:51:05,280 --> 00:51:06,320
To je identitet.

757
00:51:06,400 --> 00:51:08,480
Ako koristite Surf Line, surfer ste.

758
00:51:08,800 --> 00:51:09,440
To je ono što jeste.

759
00:51:10,320 --> 00:51:11,440
To je ono što se identificira.

760
00:51:11,680 --> 00:51:15,520
Ako koristite TeamSnap, vjerojatno ste strastveni trener mladih sportova.

761
00:51:15,600 --> 00:51:19,440
Možda vaši sinovi i kćeri igraju nogomet negdje i vi ste poput: To sam ja.

762
00:51:20,000 --> 00:51:20,880
Volim koristiti TeamSnap.

763
00:51:20,960 --> 00:51:22,240
Ako ste oneks, lovac ste.

764
00:51:22,640 --> 00:51:23,280
To je ono što jeste.

765
00:51:23,360 --> 00:51:24,160
Vi ste ljubitelj prirode.

766
00:51:24,240 --> 00:51:24,640
Vi ste grubi.

